A copyright infringement is being made on
 
the business name Swellinfo, which has been established since 2006. This
is  
the business name of the web site Swellinfo.com, as well as our other  
related products (facebook page, android/iphone app).  The App Engine  
product - http://swell-info.appspot.com/ is using the name Swell Info to  
represent their business. The infringing company is directly competing
with  
our services, which is providing surfing information and most specifically
 
information regarding current wave conditions and forecasting wave  
conditions.
